===Etymology 2===
Variant of {{m|en|worth||to become, turn into, grow, get}}, from {{inh|en|enm|worthen}}, from {{inh|en|ang|weorþan|t=to turn into, become, grow}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*werþaną|t=to turn, turn into, become}}. More at {{l|en|worth|pos=verb}}.

